title: Van Halen - 1983-05-29 - US Festival - DVD9
description: Here is a nice recent webcast with a great Red Hot Chili Peppers performance. Please enjoy, share with friends (for FREE!!!) and please seed :) I use fast servers but also need your help, there's too much downloaders to handle. I really want to share more rare stuff that is not available in shops, but i need your help to keep my collection alive. Please let your PC run for a while!!! Stuff like this needs to be preserved for future generations of music lovers. Thanks to all the peers from everywhere seeding my huge archive, i love you! ================================================================================ The 1983 US Festival, Glen Helen Park, San Bernadino, CA USA, 29th May, 1983 01) Romeo Delight 02) Unchained ~ Alex Van Halen's Drums 03) Full Bug 04) Running With The Devil 05) Jamie's Cryin' 06) So This Is Love 07) Little Guitars 08) Michael Anthony's Bass ~ Dancing In The Streets 09) Somebody Get Me A Doctor ~ Girl Gone Bad Jam ~ I'm So Glad ~ Somebody Get Me A Doctor 10) Dance The Night Away 11) Cathedral ~ Secrets 12) Everybody Wants Some 13) Ice Cream Man 14) Intruder ~ (Oh) Pretty Woman 15) Edward Van Halen's Guitar 16) Ain't Talkin' Bout Love 17) Bottoms Up 18) You Really Got Me ~ Happy Trails ~ You Really Got Me Length: 124:03min Personal: David Lee Roth: Vocals Edward Van Halen: Guitar Michael Anthony: Bass Alex Van Halen: Drums This show is for free trading only ~ if you sell you'll go to hell Van Halen, P&L https://imgur.com/9xm0gpY <<< Artwork https://imgur.com/a/k2wQm < Copyright disclaimer: fair use policy
